}}
{{end-eqn}}
Differentiating $(2)$ {{WRT|Differentiation}} $\psi$:
{{begin-eqn}}
{{eqn | l = \dfrac {\d X} {\d \psi}
      | r = \dfrac {\d x} {\d \psi} - \rho \cos \psi - \dfrac {\d \rho} {\d \psi} \sin \psi
      | c = 
