      | c = Difference Rule for Sequences in Normed Division Ring
}}
{{eqn | ll= 
      | r = x - x
}}
{{eqn | ll= 
      | r = 0_{S_1}
}}
{{eqn | o =
}}
{{eqn | ll= \leadsto
