From Corollary to Continuum Property:
:$\norm A = \inf \set {\lambda > 0: \forall h \in H: \norm {A h}_K \le \lambda \norm h_H}$ exists.
We have:
{{begin-eqn}}
{{eqn | l = \norm A
      | o = \le
